'''飓风曼努埃尔'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Manuel}}）是2013年9月在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]大部分地区引发[[洪灾|洪灾]]的破坏性[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，源于9月13日[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]以南的一片强烈[[低气压|低气压区]]，是[[2013年太平洋飓风季|这年]][[太平洋飓风季|东北太平洋]]形成的第15场获命名的风暴和第7场飓风{{#tag:ref|根据[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的定义，飓风是指持续风速在每小时119公里或以上的[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋]]和东北太平洋[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，这一标准和西北太平洋的台风相同<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}。由于高空环境有利，系统在北上期间增强成热带风暴{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带风暴是指持续风速在每小时63至118公里之间的热带气旋<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。次日，气旋迂回向西前进，并在增强至接近飓风强度后于9月15日首度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。风暴因受陆地影响快速减弱，其中心于9月16日在墨西哥上空消失。曼努埃尔的残留继续向西北方向进入[[加利福尼亚湾|加利福尼亚湾]]，于次日重新组织成热带气旋。9月18日，系统开始蜿蜒向东北方向移动，并在此期间成为热带风暴。此后不久，气旋达到飓风标准，并以最高强度从[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]以西不远处登陆。受墨西哥高山地形的影响，风暴在陆地上空迅速弱化，于9月20日清晨完全消散。

面对风暴迫在眉睫的威胁，墨西哥多个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]进入灾害预警状态。曼努埃尔首次登陆时就在墨西哥南部引发极其严重的洪灾，造成大范围财产和农业损失，估计有近100万人直接受到影响。[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]有97人丧生，其中单[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]就有18人，拉平塔达有71人因[[泥石流|泥石流]]遇难。格雷罗州有46条河流泛滥，约3万套民宅受损，全州有2万人疏散到避难所。整个格雷罗州的灾后重建耗费达30亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]。气旋的影响范围向东一直延伸到[[特万特佩克地峡|特万特佩克地峡]]，这里也有300户人家流离失所。该地区至少有1万1591套民房被洪水摧毁，墨西哥在同一时期还受到[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风]][[2013年颶風英格瑞|英格丽德]]的强烈冲击。

曼努埃尔第2次登陆后，多个城镇出现洪灾，[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]有超过10万人无家可归，4人死亡。全国范围共有428个自治区在飓风的影响下沦为灾区。锡那罗亚州一共遭受了5亿墨西哥比索的损失。风暴过后，墨西哥军队被派往多个地区协助救灾工作。抢劫在受灾最严重的地区变得司空见惯，政府为此采取行动制止此类行径。总体而言，飓风曼努埃尔一共夺走了墨西哥123人的生命，经济损失超过550亿墨西哥比索。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Manuel 2013 track.png}}
2013年8月下旬，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲海岸向西移动{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，于9月5日进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]，其轴线以北的部分之后发展成[[2013年颶風英格瑞|飓风英格丽德]]<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = David A. Zelinsky | date = 2014-01-06 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Manuel: September 13 - 19, 2013 | archivedate = 2014-12-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP132013_Manuel.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141220060116/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP132013_Manuel.pdf }}</ref>。9月10日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]宣布墨西哥西南近海在接下来几天里可能会有[[低气压|低气压]]发展，不过该系统会一直位于海洋上空<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2013-09-10 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054751/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309102319.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309102319.txt | format = TXT | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-21 }}</ref>。次日，这里发展出低气压，并且基本没有移动，其中包含的[[对流|对流]]时断时续<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 2013-09-11 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309111736.txt | format = TXT | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309111736.txt | archivedate = 2013-09-21 }}</ref>。由于系统接近陆地，还受到强烈[[风切变|风切变]]的制约，因此气象机构预计系统不会出现显著发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack L. Beven | date = 2013-09-12 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309120534.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060946/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309120534.txt | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | deadurl = no | format = TXT | accessdate = 2015-08-27 }}</ref>。9月12日，外界环境略有改观，对流的组织结构得到改善<ref>{{cite report | author = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2013-09-12 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | format = TXT | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054442/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309122326.txt | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309122326.txt }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月13日中午12点，美国国家飓风中心将系统归类为第十三{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压并开始发布公告<ref name="TCR" />，表明该天气系统中已经有足够多层次分明的环流。风切变这时已基本消失，气旋所处海域[[海面温度|水温]]也比较高，这些因素都有利于强化，只是其位置距陆地较近，还受到[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]的影响，这两项因素对热带气旋发展不利<ref>{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | date = 2013-09-13 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610230824/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-10-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-06-10 }}</ref>。

[[File:Manuel_Sept_15_2013_1725Z.jpg|thumb]]

经过短短数小时的发展，低气压快速增强成热带风暴并获名“曼努埃尔”（{{lang|en|Manuel}}）<ref name="TCR" />。到了9月14日清晨，气旋内已随[[雨带|雨带]]增长而发展出[[风眼|眼状特征]]。曼努埃尔位于东太平洋延伸到墨西哥的大规模天气系统内，[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]内的飓风英格丽德也在其中，庞大的系统带动曼努埃尔保持整体北上趋势<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2013-09-14 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Three | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710091622/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.003.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。到9月15日清晨，曼努埃尔已发展出[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]，中心的风眼有28公里宽。根据风暴结构和卫星强度估算，美国国家飓风中心估计气旋风速已达到每小时115公里，这属于风暴强度的第2波高峰{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有风速数据均为1分钟持续风速。|group="注"}}，只略低于飓风标准。该机构还指出，由于水温较高，大气环境湿润，风切变也少，风暴有可能进一步强化成飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | date = 2013-09-15 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.007.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710095636/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.007.shtml }}</ref>。受北面[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]出现微弱环节的影响，曼努埃尔起初得以继续保持整体向[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]方向移动<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie J. Berg | author2 = Richard J. Pasch | date = 2013-09-15 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710085915/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.008.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>，但在达到第2波强度高峰后，风暴转向西南方向加速前进<ref name="TCR" />。9月15日，气旋以强烈热带风暴标准从[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]西南部的阿奎拉（{{lang|en|Aquila}}）附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="TCR" />，但美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中以为曼努埃尔的登陆点是在[[科利马州|科利马州]]的[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]附近<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | author2 = David R. Zelinsky | date = 2013-09-15 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710084248/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.010.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.010.shtml? }}</ref>。9月16日清晨，环流因受陆地影响而被扰乱，风暴降级成热带低气压，但仍在产生暴雨<ref>{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi | date = 2013-09-16 | title = Tropical Depression Manuel Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.011.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710055310/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。当晚，曼努埃尔的下层环流中心在墨西哥西部上空消散<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbbie J. Berg | date = 2013-09-16 | title = Remnants of Manuel Discussion Twelve | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710061950/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.012.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.012.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。

气旋残留沿[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]上空的高压脊边缘向西北方向移动<ref name="TCR" />，于9月16日晚进入开放海域上空<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | date = 2013-09-16 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | format = TXT | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060550/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309161739.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309161739.txt }}</ref>。外界环境虽然只有小幅改善<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie J. Berg | date = 2013-09-17 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | format = TXT | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060001/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309170536.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201309170536.txt }}</ref>，但中心上空很快就有对流增长<ref name="TCR" />。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月17日下午18点，系统在重新发展出层次分明的环流后再生成热带低气压<ref name="TCR" />。气旋沿高压脊边缘缓慢向西北方向移动，外界环境有利于进一步强化，但气象部门预计低气压会在未来几天内登陆[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2013-09-17 | title = Tropical Depression Manuel Discussion Thirteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710125311/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.013.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。虽然对流格局起初杂乱无章<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael J. Brennan | date = 2013-09-18 | title = Tropical Depression Manuel Discussion Fifteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710125311/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.015.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但系统还是于9月18日再度达到热带风暴强度<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2013-09-18 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Sixteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710075404/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.016.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。当晚，对流逐渐组织，其中心发展出风眼<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2013-09-18 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Eighteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710123450/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.018.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.018.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，曼努埃尔也在{{lang|en|UTC}}9月19日凌晨0点升级成飓风<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710095821/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.public_a.018.shtml | date = 2013-09-19 | title = Hurricane Manuel Intermediate Advisory Number Eighteen-A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.public_a.018.shtml? | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>，成为1949年开始有纪录以来首场登陆墨西哥本土后再达到飓风强度的东北太平洋热带气旋<ref name="TCR" />。风暴略朝北面转向，因此与陆地间发生相互影响的时间要早于预期<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 2013-09-19 | title = Hurricane Manuel Discussion Nineteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.019.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710070836/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.019.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月19日中午12点左右，曼努埃尔以飓风强度的最低标准从[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]以西不远处登陆<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2013-09-19 | title = Hurricane Manuel Discussion Twenty-One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.021.shtml? | accessdate = 2015-08-28 | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710093246/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.021.shtml }}</ref>。进入墨西哥西部高原上空后，气旋迅速减弱成热带风暴<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2013-09-19 | title = Tropical Storm Manuel Discussion Twenty-Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.022.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-07-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710121427/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.022.shtml }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月20日凌晨0点，系统环流在[[西马德雷山脉|西马德雷山脉]]上空消散<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | date = 2013-09-20 | title = Remnants of Manuel Discussion Twenty-Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.023.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710064608/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep13/ep132013.discus.023.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-07-10 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
9月13日下午，[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]到[[拉萨罗卡德纳斯|拉萨罗卡德纳斯]]之间地区接获[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]。36小时后，由于气象机构预测曼努埃尔会在登陆前升级成飓风，拉萨罗卡德纳斯到曼萨尼约之间地区收到飓风警告。9月15日晚，飓风警告生效地区以北接获热带风暴观察预警。到了次日清晨，所有预警和警告均予中止。<ref name="TCR" />除上述预警和警告外，[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]南部还发布了“橙色”预警，该州其它地区和[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]则进入黄色预警生效状态。[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]、[[科利马州|科利马州]]、[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]、[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]和[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]部分地区进入级别较低的预警状态<ref name="EN1">{{cite news | title = La tormenta tropical "Manuel" pone en alerta a estados del suroeste de México | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201220114/http://www.el-nacional.com/mundo/tormenta-tropical-Manuel-suroeste-Mexico_0_263973747.html | url = http://www.el-nacional.com/mundo/tormenta-tropical-Manuel-suroeste-Mexico_0_263973747.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Nacional | date = 2013-09-14 | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。米却肯州的拉萨罗卡德纳斯和阿特亚加（{{lang|en|Arteaga}}）有25户居民疏散<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829012010/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/damnificados-950885.html | title = Evacuan a familias damnificadas de Michoacán | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-15 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/damnificados-950885.html | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月17日，科利马州的学校全部停课<ref name="CN6">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625145100/http://colimanoticias.com/por-la-seguridad-del-alumnado-se-suspenden-las-clases-en-todos-los-niveles-escolares-grl/ | archivedate = 2014-06-25 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | date = 2013-09-16 | url = http://colimanoticias.com/por-la-seguridad-del-alumnado-se-suspenden-las-clases-en-todos-los-niveles-escolares-grl/ | title = Por la seguridad del alumnado, se suspenden las clases en todos los niveles escolares en el Estado: | accessdate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>。

曼努埃尔在[[加利福尼亚湾|加利福尼亚湾]]重新发展成热带气旋后，[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]以北附近地区和下加利福尼亚半岛西南部接获热带风暴观察预警。次日，[[托波洛万波|托波洛万波]]（{{lang|en|Topolobampo}}）以南地区进入飓风观察预警生效状态。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月18日晚上21点，飓风观察预警升级成飓风警告。与此同时，飓风观察预警生效地区以南直至马萨特兰之间地区收到热带风暴警告。9月19日晚风暴登陆后，所以预警和警告均予中止。<ref name="TCR" />

9月18日，首度面临气旋威胁的[[索诺拉州|索诺拉州]]有13个自治区进入警戒状态<ref>{{cite news | title = Activan alertas por tormenta Manuel en Sonora | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829013713/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/activan-alertas-por-manuel-en-sonora-951508.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/activan-alertas-por-manuel-en-sonora-951508.html | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。下加利福尼亚半岛海岸沿线有7个港口关闭<ref name="EU30" />。[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]、[[卡波圣卢卡斯|卡波圣卢卡斯]]（{{lang|en|Cabo San Lucas}}）和[[圣荷西得卡波|圣荷西得卡波]]（{{lang|en|San José del Cabo}}）的港品均禁止小型船只通航和夜间出海<ref name="EU21">{{cite news | title = BCS cierra tres puertos por tormenta Manuel | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/bcs-cierra-tres-puertos-por-tormenta-manuel-951534.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829035623/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/bcs-cierra-tres-puertos-por-tormenta-manuel-951534.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>。[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]南部发布黄色预警信号，该州北部则进入绿色预警生效状态<ref name="EU22">{{cite news | title = Manuel mantiene rumbo a BCS; hay 8 estados en alerta | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829035955/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-alerta-estados-951598.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-alerta-estados-951598.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>。锡那罗亚州的学校停课<ref>{{cite news | title = Malova llama a suspender clases en Sinaloa por 'Manuel' | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829040216/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/malova-llama-a-suspender-clases-en-sinaloa-por-39manuel-39-951892.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/malova-llama-a-suspender-clases-en-sinaloa-por-39manuel-39-951892.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>，该州有700人在风暴登陆前撤离<ref name="EU32">{{cite news | title = Evacuan a más de 700 personas de Angostura y Navolato | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829055148/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/evacuan-a-mas-de-700-personas-de-angostura-y-navolato-951931.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/evacuan-a-mas-de-700-personas-de-angostura-y-navolato-951931.html }}</ref>，其中两个自治区就有365个市民疏散<ref name="EU28">{{cite news | title = Inician en Sinaloa evacuaciones ante cercanía de Manuel | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-sinaloa-951813.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829055418/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-sinaloa-951813.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>。[[纳沃拉托_(锡那罗亚州)|纳沃拉托]]有超过60户家庭撤离<ref name="NPR">{{cite news | title = Manuel A Hurricane After Deadly Mexico Flooding | archivedate = 2013-10-05 | url = http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=223836651 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005223933/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=223836651 | accessdate = 2013-10-05 | newspaper = NPR | date = 2013-10-05 | agency = Associated Press }}</ref>。锡那罗亚州同样进入橙色预警生效状态<ref name="EU33">{{cite news | title = Sinaloa, en alerta naranja por el huracán Manuel | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/sinaloa-en-alerta-naranja-por-el-huracan-manuel-951891.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829055726/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.