大概就在曼努埃尔首次登陆期间，大西洋飓风英格丽德也沿墨西哥东海岸登陆，这也是1958年以来首次有两个热带气旋在24小时内袭击墨西哥<ref name="RW1">{{cite news | title = Rare twin storms batter Mexico, 40 dead | agency = Agence France-Presse | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-tropical-storm-combine-kill-21-mexico | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829061454/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-tropical-storm-combine-kill-21-mexico | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Allan Garcia | date = 2013-09-17 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，该国蒙受的损失数额超过550亿墨西哥比索<ref name="Steve Jakubowski">{{cite web | author = Steve Jakubowski | author2 = Adityam Krovvidi | author3 = Adam Podlaha | author4 = Steve Bowen | title = September 2013 Global Catasrophe Recap | publisher = AON Benefield | work = Impact Forecasting | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140924224107/http://thoughtleadership.aonbenfield.com/Documents/20131007_if_september_global_recap.pdf | url = http://thoughtleadership.aonbenfield.com/Documents/20131007_if_september_global_recap.pdf | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-09-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，其中单道路所受破坏价值就达20亿墨西哥比索<ref name="CN11">{{cite news | title = Ascienden a más de 2 mdp los daños de vialidades por Tormenta "Manuel" | date = 2013-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archivedate = 2014-06-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625133618/http://colimanoticias.com/se-atienden-a-30-personas-en-albergue-instalado-en-el-chavarin/ | url = http://colimanoticias.com/se-atienden-a-30-personas-en-albergue-instalado-en-el-chavarin/ }}</ref>。飓风曼努埃尔一共夺走123条人命，其中104人属风暴直接导致<ref name="TCR" />。该国有约5万9000人疏散，其中3万9000人躲进避难所<ref name="RWES">{{cite report | title = Reunión de Evaluación de la situación en el estado de Guerrero, encabezada por el Presidente de la República, Enrique Peña Nieto. | publisher = ReliefWeb | work = Mexican Government | date = 2013-09-18 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407065244/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Mexico_Info%20Note%20Remnants%20of%20Ingrid%20and%20Manuel%20Number%202_As%20of%20Wednesday%2018%20Sept%202013.pdf | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Mexico_Info%20Note%20Remnants%20of%20Ingrid%20and%20Manuel%20Number%202_As%20of%20Wednesday%2018%20Sept%202013.pdf }}</ref>。有约100万人直接受到曼努埃尔的影响<ref name="NBCN">{{cite news | title = Looting hits Acapulco as Mexico storm death toll reaches 80 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417185306/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/other/looting-hits-acapulco-mexico-storm-death-toll-reaches-80-f4B11189408 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = NBC News | date = 2013-09-18 | author = Alberto Fajardo and Luis Enrique Martinez | archivedate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/other/looting-hits-acapulco-mexico-storm-death-toll-reaches-80-f4B11189408 }}</ref>。

受飓风曼努埃尔影响，墨西哥大部分地区在长达7天的时间里普降暴雨，特别是该国山区，飓风英格丽德和大范围的西南向[[季风|季风]]也助长了雨势。多地降雨量超过250毫米，其中格雷罗州圣伊西德罗测得的降雨量最高，达1110毫米。附近的阿卡普尔科测得的降雨量也有450毫米。更北面的米却肯州最高降雨量为562毫米。气旋第2次登陆后，[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]降下470毫米雨量，附近的桑那罗纳（{{lang|en|Sanalona}}）降水也达到389毫米<ref name="TCR" />。

=== 瓦哈卡州 ===
吉卡扬（{{lang|en|Jicayan}}）有10套民房因风暴受损，1所学校被淹，报道还称海上有1艘船失踪<ref name="EU2">{{cite news | title = Tormenta Manuel Inundaciones Deslaves en Acapulco | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-14 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-manuel-inundaciones-deslaves-950747.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829084308/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-manuel-inundaciones-deslaves-950747.html | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>。[[特万特佩克地峡|特万特佩克地峡]]沿岸有300户居民无家可归<ref>{{cite news |title=Oaxaca en alerta por derrumbes en carreteras e inundaciones |url=http://www.tvnws.com/2013/09/14/oaxaca-en-alerta-por-derrumbes-en-carreteras-e-inundaciones/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oaxaca-en-alerta-por-derrumbes-en-carreteras-e-inundaciones |accessdate=2013-09-15 |newspaper=Telenews |date=2013-09-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130915054151/http://www.tvnws.com/2013/09/14/oaxaca-en-alerta-por-derrumbes-en-carreteras-e-inundaciones/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oaxaca-en-alerta-por-derrumbes-en-carreteras-e-inundaciones |archivedate=2013-09-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。风暴还令约5000只动物死亡<ref name="CNN3">{{cite news | title = La cifra de muertos en Guerrero sube a 72 tras afectaciones por 'Manuel' | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = CNN Mexico | date = 2013-09-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150815151600/http://mexico.cnn.com/nacional/2013/09/18/70-personas-desaparecen-en-guerrero-por-un-alud-en-el-municipio-de-atoyac | archivedate = 2015-08-15 | deadurl = yes | url = http://mexico.cnn.com/nacional/2013/09/18/70-personas-desaparecen-en-guerrero-por-un-alud-en-el-municipio-de-atoyac }}</ref>。瓦哈卡州共有200公顷农作物被毁，不过全州遭受的破坏程度总体不及格雷罗州<ref>{{cite news | title = Considera Cué superada la emergencia por lluvias en Oaxaca | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/cue-oaxaca-lluvias-emergencia-952373.html | date = 2013-09-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829102300/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/cue-oaxaca-lluvias-emergencia-952373.html | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。瓦哈卡州有19个社区同外界的联络中断<ref name="EU40">{{cite news | title = Suman 13 mil incomunicados en Oaxaca | date = 2013-09-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829102454/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-trece-mil-incomunicados-oaxaca-952544.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-trece-mil-incomunicados-oaxaca-952544.html }}</ref>，共计4人丧生<ref name="CF">{{cite web | title = Cifras de la tragedia | publisher = Excelisor | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150507094355/http://www.excelsior.com.mx/especial/lluvias/el-saldo-del-2013 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.excelsior.com.mx/especial/lluvias/el-saldo-del-2013 | work = Cifras | archivedate = 2015-05-07 }}</ref>。全州有77个自治区受到风暴引发的洪灾影响<ref name="RW5" />，约1万人受灾<ref name="SG2">{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140607001341/http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Archivos/Documentos/2013/10/asun_3013436_20131003_1380836906.pdf | title = AGENDA POLíTICA SOBRE COMENTARIOS RELATIVOS A LA SITUACIóN DE EMERGENCIA PROVOCADA POR LOS DAÑOS OCURRIDOS EN DIVERSAS ENTIDADES DEL PAíS | publisher = Secretaría de Gobernación | date = 2013-10 | archivedate = 2014-06-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Archivos/Documentos/2013/10/asun_3013436_20131003_1380836906.pdf }}</ref>。

=== 格雷罗州 ===
[[File:EPN._Afectados_tormenta_Manue_en_Acapulco.jpg|thumbnail]][[恩里克·佩尼亚·涅托|恩里克·佩尼亚·涅托]]和内政部长米格尔·安赫尔·奥索里奥·庄在[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]周边灾区视察。]]

格雷罗州至少有97人遇难<ref name="TCR" />，约3万套住宅受损<ref name="BBC 2">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-24296433 | title = La Pintada: the village wiped from the map of Mexico | date = 2013-09-27 | agency = BBC News | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Will Grant | archivedate = 2014-11-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141112080522/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-24296433 }}</ref>，其中1万1591套房屋遭受的破坏程度较为严重<ref name="RW5">{{cite report | title = MéXICO – Ingrid y Manuel – Septiembre 2013 1 MéXICO – Info Note Rem n ants of “Ingrid” and “Manuel ” | publisher = ReliefWeb | work = National Disaster Response Advisor | date = 2013-09-18 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2014-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407065244/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Mexico_Info%20Note%20Remnants%20of%20Ingrid%20and%20Manuel%20Number%202_As%20of%20Wednesday%2018%20Sept%202013.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Mexico_Info%20Note%20Remnants%20of%20Ingrid%20and%20Manuel%20Number%202_As%20of%20Wednesday%2018%20Sept%202013.pdf }}</ref>。被毁的民房至少有1万1000套<ref name="TT" />，2万人撤离到避难所躲避<ref name="EU25" />，其中有1万2000人分布在47个避难所内<ref name="TT">{{cite news | title = Deadly tropical storms wreak havoc across Mexico | date = 2013-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503075108/http://thetequilafiles.com/2013/09/17/jalisco-suffers-as-tropical-storms-wreak-havoc-across-mexico/ | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = The Tequilafiles | deadurl = no | url = http://thetequilafiles.com/2013/09/17/jalisco-suffers-as-tropical-storms-wreak-havoc-across-mexico/ }}</ref>。全州有24条河流泛滥<ref name="RW5" />，至少32条道路受损，4座桥梁倒塌<ref name="EU25">{{cite news | title = La recuperación será costosa, estima Segob | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829104107/http://www.lapoliciaca.com/nota-roja/lluvias-golpean-24-estados-sigue-alerta/ | url = http://www.lapoliciaca.com/nota-roja/lluvias-golpean-24-estados-sigue-alerta/ | archivedate = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>。

阿卡普尔科以西的边远渔村拉平塔达（{{lang|en|La Pintada}}）生活有约400居民<ref name="RW4">{{cite news | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mudslide-buries-village-new-hurricane-nears-mexico | title = Mudslide buries village as Hurricane Manuel lashes Mexico | date = 2013-09-19 | agency = Agence France-Presse | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182556/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mudslide-buries-village-new-hurricane-nears-mexico | author = Leticia Pineda | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，9月14日这里发生[[泥石流|泥石流]]，只花几分钟时间就席卷了镇中心。许多居民怀着恐慌和迷惑在镇上徘徊，<ref name="BBC 2" />直到两天后有关泥石流的消息才逐渐为大众所知<ref name="RW7">{{cite news | date = 2013-09-19 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182700/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-death-toll-nears-100-new-hurricane-hits | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-death-toll-nears-100-new-hurricane-hits | title = Mexico death toll nears 100 as new hurricane hits | agency = Agence France-Presse | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Leticia Pineda | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-03 }}</ref>。整个村庄有71人丧生<ref name="YE">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-05-31 | url = https://news.yahoo.com/homes-mexican-village-landslide-221716802.html | title = New homes for Mexican village after landslide | date = 2014-05-26 | agency = Yahoo News | accessdate = 2014-05-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140531033243/http://news.yahoo.com/homes-mexican-village-landslide-221716802.html }}</ref>，有过半区域被泥石流摧毁，其中还包括20套民宅，警方共计疏散了334人<ref name="RW4" />，有30人经选中后留在当地，直至所有遇难者的身份确认为止<ref name="RW8">{{cite news | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/rescuers-resume-search-victims-mexico-mudslide | title = Rescuers to resume search for victims of Mexico mudslide | agency = Agence France-Presse | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Leticia Pineda | date = 2013-09-20 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182628/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/rescuers-resume-search-victims-mexico-mudslide | deadurl = no }}</ref>。拉平塔达的幸存者中有许多都受了伤，其中1人重伤<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news |title=Hurricane Manuel hits land in northern Mexico |date=2013-09-19 |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2015-08-29 |author=Weissenstein, Mark |newspaper=USA Today |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140605005203/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/09/19/mexico-olandslide-storm/2835077/ |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/09/19/mexico-olandslide-storm/2835077/ |archivedate=2014-06-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

阿特拉马哈尔辛戈德尔蒙特自治区有1名女性因住房倒塌死亡<ref name="EU5">{{cite news | title = Suspenden "el Grito" en Guerrero por afectaciones | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-afectaciones-grito-950854.html | accessdate = 2014-03-01 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-15 | archivedate = 2014-03-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140301012821/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-afectaciones-grito-950854.html | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。格雷罗州首府[[奇尔潘辛戈|奇尔潘辛戈]]有4人遇难<ref name="EU8">{{cite news | title = Lluvias incomunican Chilpancingo; se dificulta ayuda | accessdate = 2014-02-02 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-16 | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/chilpancingo-lluvias-incomunicado-951018.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202120345/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/chilpancingo-lluvias-incomunicado-951018.html | archivedate = 2014-02-02 }}</ref>。许多树木倒塌，多地报告停电。此外，附近的塞里托黎各大坝也几近决堤<ref name="EU7">{{cite news | title = Chilpancingo, en emergencia por lluvias intensas | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/chilpancingo-en-emergencia-por-lluvias-intensas-950828.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202120345/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/chilpancingo-lluvias-incomunicado-951018.html | deadurl = no | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-15 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 }}</ref>。特克潘（{{lang|es|Tecpán}}）自治区有4条河流泛滥成灾，6人因山体滑坡丧生<ref name=RW1 />。许多山地社区与世隔绝，难以获得援助<ref name="BBC 2" />。

==== 阿卡普尔科 ====
[[File:Resultados_del_Huracán_Ingrid_y_tormenta_Manuel_(Acapulco,_Guerrero)_23.JPG|thumb]]

阿卡普尔科市的受灾情况最为严重<ref name="EU3" />，[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]在报道中称曼努埃尔是多年来对墨西哥破坏最严重的风暴<ref name="NBCN" />。该市有18人死亡<ref name="IN">{{cite news | title = Al menos 80 muertos, 58 desaparecidos y nuevo huracán en México | newspaper = Infonews | date = 2013-09-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202102206/http://www.infonews.com/2013/09/19/mundo-98540-al-menos-80-muertos-58-desaparecidos-y-nuevo-huracan-en-mexico.php | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | url = http://www.infonews.com/2013/09/19/mundo-98540-al-menos-80-muertos-58-desaparecidos-y-nuevo-huracan-en-mexico.php | access-date = 2015-08-29 }}</ref>，其中1人是被倒塌的围墙压死<ref name="EU5" />。附近发生的一场车祸夺走了6名游客的生命，其中还有两名未成年人<ref name="EU3">{{cite news | title = Tormenta Manuel deja 21 muertos en Guerrero | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-manuel-causa-21-muertos-en-guerrero-950907.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014051833/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-manuel-causa-21-muertos-en-guerrero-950907.html | accessdate = 2013-10-14 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-15 | archivedate = 2013-10-14 }}</ref>，这场车祸还令两段围栏和一艘船受损，导致另外两人受伤<ref name="EU1">{{cite news | title = Suman siete los muertos por lluvias en Guerrero | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-siete-los-muertos-por-lluvias-en-guerrero-950772.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-14 | archivedate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829122434/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-siete-los-muertos-por-lluvias-en-guerrero-950772.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。阿卡普尔科附近河流泛滥，导致邻近社区的多套民居被淹<ref name="EU1" />。另据报道，当地发生数起相互间没有发现关联的人为破坏事件<ref name="RW5" />，还出现两起泥石流，造成一户民宅被毁，几条道路封闭<ref name="GI1">{{cite news | title = "Manuel" deja inundaciones y deslaves en Acapulco | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054159/http://guanajuatoinforma.com/index.php/noticias/nacional/14110-manuel-deja-inundaciones-y-deslaves-en-acapulco | accessdate = 2013-09-21 | newspaper = Guanajuato Informa | date = 2013-09-14 | url = http://guanajuatoinforma.com/index.php/noticias/nacional/14110-manuel-deja-inundaciones-y-deslaves-en-acapulco | author = SUN | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。阿卡普尔科有一套民房因山体滑坡被毁，一家6口全部遇难<ref name="RW1" />。至少4万名在阿卡普尔科度过[[多洛雷斯呼声|墨西哥独立日]]的游客因机场被淹而困在当地<ref name="NBCN" /><ref name="EU12">{{cite news | title = Suman 40 mil turistas varados en Acapulco: Robles | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-40-mil-turistas-varados-en-acapulco-robles-951107.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140301003349/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-40-mil-turistas-varados-en-acapulco-robles-951107.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，离开该市的几条主要道路都因山体滑坡而封闭<ref name="RL">{{cite news | title = At least 58 missing after mudslide hits Mexico ahead of hurricane | url = http://www.rt.com/news/mexico-mudslide-missing-hurricane-050/ | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = RL News | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202165623/http://rt.com/news/mexico-mudslide-missing-hurricane-050/ }}</ref>。截至9月19日，军方已利用飞机将1万人转移到[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]<ref name="USA Today" />，但由于[[雷达|雷达]]无法正常使用，这一疏散工作面临困境<ref name="RW2">{{cite news | title = Acapulco airlift begins as storms toll rises | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/acapulco-airlift-begins-storms-toll-rises | agency = Agence France-Presse | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182617/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/acapulco-airlift-begins-storms-toll-rises | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Allan Garcia | date = 2013-09-18 }}</ref>。整个阿卡普尔科一共有1万3516套住宅受损<ref name="CNN3" />。

=== 科利马州 ===
科利马州的洪灾程度较轻<ref>{{cite news | title = Declaran emergencia por lluvia en Guerrero | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054046/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/primera-plana/2013/impreso/declaran-emergencia-por-lluvia-en-guerrero-43028.html | newspaper = El Universal | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | date = 2013-09-16 | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/primera-plana/2013/impreso/declaran-emergencia-por-lluvia-en-guerrero-43028.html | archivedate = 2013-09-21 }}</ref>，沙纳尔（{{lang|en|Chanal}}）的降雨量全州最高，有144毫米<ref name="CN3">{{cite news | url = http://colimanoticias.com/reporta-pc-nivel-de-rios-y-arroyos-estables-en-la-capital/ | title = Reporta PC nivel de ríos y arroyos estables en la capital | date = 2013-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625145816/http://colimanoticias.com/reporta-pc-nivel-de-rios-y-arroyos-estables-en-la-capital/ | archivedate = 2014-06-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。多户家庭被迫撤离<ref name="EU10">{{cite news | title = Manuel azota Colima; evacuan a familias | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-colima-lluvias-951049.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-16 | archivedate = 2014-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416230459/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-colima-lluvias-951049.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，州内许多水坝的蓄水量都已到达极限<ref name="EU17">{{cite news | title = Presas de Colima llegan a su máxima capacidad | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-17 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/presas-de-colima-llegan-a-su-maxima-capacidad-951388.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925191313/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/presas-de-colima-llegan-a-su-maxima-capacidad-951388.html | archivedate = 2013-09-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，许多通往曼萨尼约机场的道路封闭<ref name="EU18">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416212033/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/sigue-cerrado-el-aeropuerto-de-manzanillo-951471.html | title = Sigue cerrado el aeropuerto de Manzanillo | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/sigue-cerrado-el-aeropuerto-de-manzanillo-951471.html | deadurl = no | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>。伊斯特拉瓦坎（{{lang|en|Ixtlahuacán}}）有50户家庭因河流泛滥的威胁而疏散<ref name="CN1">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625180524/http://colimanoticias.com/no-se-han-registrado-muertes-por-tormenta-manuel/ | url = http://colimanoticias.com/no-se-han-registrado-muertes-por-tormenta-manuel/ | title = No se han registrado muertes por tormenta "Manuel" | date = 2013-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>，另外30户则被送往该州其他地区的避难所<ref name="CN5">{{cite news | newspaper = Colima Noticias | url = http://colimanoticias.com/se-atienden-a-30-personas-en-albergue-instalado-en-el-chavarin/ | title = Se atienden a 30 personas en albergue instalado en El Chavarín | date = 2013-09-16 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625133618/http://colimanoticias.com/se-atienden-a-30-personas-en-albergue-instalado-en-el-chavarin/ | archivedate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>。[[阿尔瓦雷斯镇_(科利马州)|阿尔瓦雷斯镇]]有一座桥梁倒塌<ref name="CN8">{{cite news | url = http://colimanoticias.com/reportan-hundimiento-en-puente-deprimido/ | title = Reportan hundimiento en puente deprimido | date = 2013-09-17 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625173632/http://colimanoticias.com/reportan-hundimiento-en-puente-deprimido/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>。该州还有一名男子因试图过河而遇难<ref name="EU41">{{cite news | title = Suman mil 600 damnificados en Colima por 'Manuel' | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504015604/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-mil-600-damnificados-en-colima-por-39manuel-39-952367.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archivedate = 2014-05-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/suman-mil-600-damnificados-en-colima-por-39manuel-39-952367.html }}</ref>。4棵大树被刮倒<ref name="CN2">{{cite news | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625135914/http://colimanoticias.com/supervisa-tito-vazquez-comunidades-y-colonias-por-paso-de-depresion-tropical-manuel/ | title = No se han registrado muertes por tormenta "Manuel" | date = 2013-09-16 | deadurl = no | url = http://colimanoticias.com/supervisa-tito-vazquez-comunidades-y-colonias-por-paso-de-depresion-tropical-manuel/ | archivedate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>，风暴还摧毁了约1万5000公顷香蕉作物<ref name="CN10">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625180634/http://colimanoticias.com/calculan-15-mil-hectareas-danadas-de-limon-tras-el-paso-de-manuel/ | url = http://colimanoticias.com/calculan-15-mil-hectareas-danadas-de-limon-tras-el-paso-de-manuel/ | title = Calculan 15 mil hectáreas dañadas de limón tras el paso de "Manuel" | date = 2013-09-19 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archivedate = 2014-06-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。总体而言，科利马州以伊斯特拉瓦坎、[[特科曼|特科曼]]、曼萨尼约和科马拉（{{lang|en|Comala}}）受灾最为严重<ref name="CN7">{{cite news | newspaper = Colima Noticias | url = http://colimanoticias.com/calcularan-danos-por-manuel-para-solicitar-recursos-al-fonden/ | title = Calcularán daños por "Manuel" para solicitar recursos al Fonden | date = 2013-09-17 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625141906/http://colimanoticias.com/calcularan-danos-por-manuel-para-solicitar-recursos-al-fonden/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>，飓风曼努埃尔也成为[[1959年墨西哥飓风|1959年墨西哥飓风]]以来对科利马州产生破坏最严重的风暴<ref name="CN9">{{cite news | date = 2013-09-18 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625163157/http://colimanoticias.com/tormenta-tropical-manuel-dejo-danos-similares-a-los-del-ciclon-de-1959-federico-rangel/ | title = Tormenta tropical "Manuel" dejó daños similares a los del ciclón de 1959: Federico Rangel | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archivedate = 2014-06-25 | deadurl = no | url = http://colimanoticias.com/tormenta-tropical-manuel-dejo-danos-similares-a-los-del-ciclon-de-1959-federico-rangel/ }}</ref>，该州的损失总额超过4亿7900万墨西哥比索<ref name="CN12">{{cite news | title = Daños totales por "Manuel" superan los 477 MdP | date = 2013-10-09 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = Colima Noticias | archivedate = 2014-06-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625160409/http://colimanoticias.com/danos-totales-por-manuel-superan-los-477-mdp/ | url = http://colimanoticias.com/danos-totales-por-manuel-superan-los-477-mdp/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 哈利斯科州 ===
更北面的哈利斯科州出现轻度洪灾<ref name="EU4">{{cite news | title = Evacuan jaliscienses zonas de riesgo por lluvias | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/evacuan-jaliscienses-zonas-de-riesgo-950900.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417002610/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/evacuan-jaliscienses-zonas-de-riesgo-950900.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-15 | archivedate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，全州有4人死亡。[[胡安娜卡特兰|胡安娜卡特兰]]（{{lang|en|Juanacatlan}}）1名26岁男子被洪水卷走后身亡，特奥库蒂特兰德科罗纳1名12岁男童因跌入水坝溺毙。库奥蒂特兰（{{lang|en|Cuautitlan de Garcia Barragan}}）还有1名男子因车冲入山沟而遇难。哈利斯科州共有1500人从家中撤离，588所学校停课，超过4万名学子因此待在家里。州内有多座桥梁倒塌，该州以南部、[[瓜达拉哈拉_(墨西哥)|瓜达拉哈拉]]以及沿海地区受灾最为严重，部分区域发生洪灾和山体滑坡<ref>{{cite news | url = http://thetequilafiles.com/2013/09/17/jalisco-suffers-as-tropical-storms-wreak-havoc-across-mexico/ | title = Jalisco suffers as Manuel batters western Mexico | date = 2013-09-17 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503075108/http://thetequilafiles.com/2013/09/17/jalisco-suffers-as-tropical-storms-wreak-havoc-across-mexico/ | newspaper = The Tequilafiles | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。整个哈利斯科州一共有56个自治区受灾<ref>{{cite news | title = Sinaloa reporta primera muerte por Manuel | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503075108/http://thetequilafiles.com/2013/09/17/jalisco-suffers-as-tropical-storms-wreak-havoc-across-mexico/ | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-muerto-sinaloa-952141.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 锡那罗亚州 ===
曼努埃尔第2次登陆前不久，特帕奇特兰有1名渔夫丧生<ref name="EU23">{{cite news | title = Reportan primera muerte por lluvias en Zacatecas | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/zacatecas-lluvia-deceso-951620.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023061018/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/zacatecas-lluvia-deceso-951620.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，还有1人因从捕虾船上摔下而遇难<ref name="EU36" />。1名卡车司机和1个年仅5岁的孩子死亡，孩子的母亲失踪<ref name="EU37" />。马萨特兰、罗萨里奥（{{lang|es|El Rosario}}）和埃斯昆纳帕（{{lang|es|Escuinapa}}）出现洪灾<ref name="NPR" />。安戈斯图拉（{{lang|en|Angostura}}）、[[莫科里托|莫科里托]]（{{lang|en|Mocorito}}）、纳沃拉托和库利亚坎被洪水淹没，引起中等程度破坏。安戈斯图拉有许多居民被困在自家屋顶，纳沃拉托沿海地区被淹，有关部门称有500人无家可归<ref name="EU34" />，数以百计的树木倒塌，多条输电线缆中断<ref name="EU35">{{cite news | title = Manuel derriba árboles y deja sin luz a sinaloenses | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224125447/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel--951960.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel--951960.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2014-02-24 }}</ref>。受河道溢流的影响，莫科里托部分地区与世隔绝<ref name="EU34" />，市里的积水和堆叠的垃圾有2米深<ref>{{cite news | title = Registra Mocorito inundaciones de hasta 2 metros | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/registra-mocorito-inundaciones-de-hasta-2-metros-952303.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-20 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202121011/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/registra-mocorito-inundaciones-de-hasta-2-metros-952303.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。库利亚坎的洪灾程度较轻<ref name="EU34">{{cite news | title = Afecta Manuel a cuatro municipios de Sinaloa | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140227094029/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/afecta-manuel-a-cuatro-municipios-de-sinaloa-951953.html | archivedate = 2014-02-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/afecta-manuel-a-cuatro-municipios-de-sinaloa-951953.html }}</ref>。辛尼托几乎所有的道路都被摧毁<ref name="EU36">{{cite news | title = Manuel deja incomunicados a municipios en Sinaloa | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-incomunica-poblados-sianloa-952188.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223190530/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/manuel-incomunica-poblados-sianloa-952188.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，海上还有24艘船受损<ref name="CNN2" />。整个锡那罗亚州共有10万人流离失所<ref name="EU37">{{cite news | title = En Sinaloa, tormenta mata a tres | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228034851/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion-mexico/2013/impreso/en-sinaloa-tormenta-mata-a-tres-209232.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-20 | archivedate = 2014-02-28 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion-mexico/2013/impreso/en-sinaloa-tormenta-mata-a-tres-209232.html }}</ref>，共3000人疏散到62个避难所。全州有70个社区受到这场风暴的破坏<ref name="CNN2">{{cite news | title = 100,000 afectados en Sinaloa por el paso del huracán 'Manuel | newspaper = CNN Mexico | date = 2013-09-19 | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | url = http://mexico.cnn.com/nacional/2013/09/20/huracan-manuel-muertos-afectados-damnificados-sinaloa | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150815151524/http://mexico.cnn.com/nacional/2013/09/20/huracan-manuel-muertos-afectados-damnificados-sinaloa | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2015-08-15 }}</ref>，有10个自治区的14万6000居民直接受到曼努埃尔的影响<ref name="EU39">{{cite news | title = Aumenta número de damnificados en Sinaloa | date = 2013-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202121013/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/aumenta-numero-de-damnificados-en-sinaloa-952511.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/aumenta-numero-de-damnificados-en-sinaloa-952511.html }}</ref>，经济损失总额达5亿墨西哥比索<ref name="EU38">{{cite news | title = Calculan en Sinaloa daños por 500 mdp | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202120917/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion-mexico/2013/impreso/calculan-en-sinaloa-danios-por-500-mdp-209268.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-22 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion-mexico/2013/impreso/calculan-en-sinaloa-danios-por-500-mdp-209268.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-02 }}</ref>。

=== 其它地区 ===
米却肯州出现洪灾，许多人只能等待空中救援<ref name="EU24">{{cite news | title = Rescatan vía aérea a damnificados en Michoacán | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/michoacan-puente-aereo-damnificados-951648.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416215448/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/michoacan-puente-aereo-damnificados-951648.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，该州经报道有两人遇难<ref name="CF" />。[[杜兰戈州|杜兰戈州]]有42套民宅受损<ref name="EU16">{{cite news | title = Lluvias dejan 42 viviendas afectadas en Durango | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/lluvias-durango-casas-951244.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416215049/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/lluvias-durango-casas-951244.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-17 | archivedate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，导致50位居民被困<ref name="EU38" />。气旋掠过[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]期间，[[拉巴斯_(南下加利福尼亚州)|拉巴斯]]测得0.61米高的海浪，风速则为每小时42公里<ref name="EU30">{{cite news | title = Cierran 7 puertos en BCS por tormenta tropical Manuel | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023060814/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/puertos-bcs-manuel-prevencion-951833.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/puertos-bcs-manuel-prevencion-951833.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。锡那罗亚州的最高降雨量出现在库利亚坎，达415毫米<ref name="EU37" />。曼努埃尔消散后的残留还给[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]大范围地区带去充沛雨量<ref name="NWSBRO">{{cite web | title = Sun(light) at the End of the Tunnel? (We Mean It This Time) What's Next for the RGV | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/images/bro/news/2013/pdf/September21_23_Impacts_09202013_2PMCDT.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925150720/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/images/bro/news/2013/pdf/September21_23_Impacts_09202013_2PMCDT.pdf | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = National Weather Service Office at Brownsville, Texas | location = Brownsville, Texas | date = 2013-09-20 | archivedate = 2013-09-25 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]的水分和逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]令降水进一步增多<ref name="NASASees">{{cite web | title = NASA sees remnants of Hurricane Manuel soaking northern Mexico, Texas | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Phys.org | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150324223605/http://phys.org/news/2013-09-nasa-remnants-hurricane-manuel-northern.html | publisher = Phys.org | url = http://phys.org/news/2013-09-nasa-remnants-hurricane-manuel-northern.html | date = 2013-09-20 | archivedate = 2015-03-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]地区因此出现局部洪灾，多条[[沉下橋|沉下橋]]被迫封闭。9月20日，位于[[马布里军营|马布里军营]]的气象站测得74毫米降水，创下该站的单日纪录<ref name="ATXFlood">{{cite web | title = Flash flood watch canceled; sunny Saturday expected | url = http://www.statesman.com/news/weather/rain-now-rain-likely-later-today/nZ3Xr/ | publisher = Austin American Statesmen | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | author = Beach, Patrick; Forbes-Robards, Esther; Womack, Sam | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140713182931/http://www.statesman.com/news/weather/rain-now-rain-likely-later-today/nZ3Xr/ | archivedate = 2014-07-13 | location = Austin, Texas | date = 2013-09-20 }}</ref>。根据雷达数据估算，德克萨斯州西部局部地区的降雨量有可能高达200毫米<ref name="NWSBRO" />。[[金布尔县_(得克萨斯州)|金布尔县]]有一条公路因洪水封闭。[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]中部普遍测得51至114毫米降水<ref>{{cite journal |deadurl=yes |format=PDF |url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-56BF3049-6902-4F21-BA39-B88116A87382.pdf |volume=55 |title=September 2013 Storm Data |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QjQ6EG6F?url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-56BF3049-6902-4F21-BA39-B88116A87382.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-01 |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |issue=9 |journal= }}</ref>。

