风暴过去后，阿卡普尔科进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="EU11">{{cite news | title = Peña Nieto viaja por emergencia a Acapulco | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion-mexico/2013/vero-951095.html | accessdate = 2015-08-29 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-16 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503030949/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion-mexico/2013/vero-951095.html }}</ref>，共有约1万2000件物品经空运送往当地<ref name="EU26">{{cite news | title = Se entregan 12 mil despensas en Guerrero: Robles | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503030833/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/pan-rechaza-reforma-hacendaria-del-gobierno-federal-951759.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/pan-rechaza-reforma-hacendaria-del-gobierno-federal-951759.html }}</ref>。格雷罗州各地一共开设了662个损赠中心<ref name="EU25" />，全州一共花费了30亿墨西哥比索修复风暴造成的破坏<ref name="EU14">{{cite news | title = Guerrero necesita al menos 5 mil mdp, estima Aguirre | date = 2013-09-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224205855/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-necesita-al-menos-5-mil-mdp-estima-aguirre-951222.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2014-02-24 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-necesita-al-menos-5-mil-mdp-estima-aguirre-951222.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。经济部长还另批了1亿墨西哥比索用于该州救灾<ref>{{cite news | title = SE apoyará con 100 mdp a negocios afectados en Guerrero | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-lluvias-se-ayuda-951616.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503043725/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/guerrero-lluvias-se-ayuda-951616.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，财政部宣布有120亿墨西哥比索资金可供使用<ref name="NBCN" />。[[墨西哥红十字会|墨西哥红十字会]]将收集到的货物运往灾区，其中又以格雷罗州占比最高<ref name="RW5" />，还提供了400万零79吨援助物资。当地部门也提供了2万9000吨个人或家居用品<ref name="RW21">{{cite report | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/cruz-roja-mexicana-envia-4-mil-079-toneladas-de-ayuda-humanitaria-estados-afectados | title = Cruz Roja Mexicana envia 4 mil 079 toneladas de ayuda humanitaria a estados afectados por Ingrid y Manuel | work = Cruz Roja Mexicana | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2013-10-07 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714133035/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/cruz-roja-mexicana-envia-4-mil-079-toneladas-de-ayuda-humanitaria-estados-afectados }}</ref>。[[无国界医生|无国界医生]]在5个避难所内分发了2800升水、食品和药品<ref name="RW5" />。国家自然灾害基金提供8700万[[欧元|欧元]]用于购买包括食品、床垫、饮用水和药物在内的必需品<ref name="RW6">{{cite report | title = ECHO Daily Map – Tropical Cyclones (as of 19 September 2013) | work = European Commission Humanitarian Aid department | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2013-09-19 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | url = http://reliefweb.int/map/mexico/echo-daily-map-%E2%80%93-tropical-cyclones-19-september-2013 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182650/http://reliefweb.int/map/mexico/echo-daily-map-%E2%80%93-tropical-cyclones-19-september-2013 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。水任务国际事工向约2万人提供饮用水<ref name="RW9">{{cite report | date = 2013-09-20 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/us-safe-water-nonprofit-aids-mexico-flood-victims | title = U.S. safe water nonprofit aids Mexico flood victims | publisher = Water Missons International | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182639/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/us-safe-water-nonprofit-aids-mexico-flood-victims }}</ref>。[[世界展望会|世界展望会]]墨西哥分会向80户家庭提供用于遮盖屋顶的塑料布，该组织还向76户家庭提供了蚊帐，还捐赠了包括大米、油、沙丁鱼、糖、盐、饼干、豆类在内的多种食品和杂货<ref name="RW10">{{cite web | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/%E2%80%9C-rains-have-decreased-emergency-continues-especially-children-and-their-families | title = The rains have decreased, but the emergency continues, especially for the children and their families in the rural communities. | publisher = ReliefWeb | work = World Vision | date = 2013-10-03 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140504050803/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/%E2%80%9C-rains-have-decreased-emergency-continues-especially-children-and-their-families | archivedate = 2014-05-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[基督复临会发展救济局|基督复临会发展救济局]]墨西哥分部是最早向灾民伸出援手的组织之一，到10月上旬时已经向8000人提供帮助<ref name="RW17">{{cite web | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/adra-responds-hurricane-ingrid-and-tropical-storm-manuel | title = ADRA Responds to Hurricane Ingrid and Tropical Storm Manuel | publisher = ReliefWeb | work = ADRA International | date = 2013-10-09 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714133548/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/adra-responds-hurricane-ingrid-and-tropical-storm-manuel }}</ref>。

瓦哈卡州有42个自治区沦为灾区<ref name="EU15">{{cite news | title = Segob declara emergencia en 42 alcaldías de Oaxaca | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/oaxaca-segob-emergencia-manuel-951238.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417013614/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/oaxaca-segob-emergencia-manuel-951238.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-17 | archivedate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，格雷罗州有56个自治区经宣示为灾区<ref name="EU20">{{cite news | title = Segob emite 56 declaratorias para Guerrero | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/declaratorias-guerrero-segob-951469.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503025224/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/declaratorias-guerrero-segob-951469.html | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-17 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，米却肯州也有9个自治区成为灾区<ref name="EU19">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503043439/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/michoacan-desastre-municipios--951444.html | title = Michoacán declara 9 municipios zonas de desastre | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/michoacan-desastre-municipios--951444.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-17 }}</ref>。整个墨西哥沦为灾区的自治区一共有428个<ref name="SG">{{cite web | archivedate = 2015-08-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150830032618/http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Archivos/Documentos/2013/12/asun_3058896_20131218_1387381362.pdf | title = De la se cretaría de gobernac ión, con la que remite contestación a punto de acuerdo aprobados por la cámara de diput ados , relativo a la liberación de los recursos financi eros destinados al fondo de desastres naturales a fin de aliviar las afectaci ones a las comunidad es de los estados de la república afectados por la tor menta manuel y el hu racán ingrid. | publisher = Secretaría de Gobernación | date = 2013-12-13 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Archivos/Documentos/2013/12/asun_3058896_20131218_1387381362.pdf }}</ref>，并且一共因飓风曼努埃尔和英格丽德发布了155次紧急声明<ref name="CNN3" />。米却肯州、哈利斯科州的21个自治区宣布进入紧急状态，不过到10月中旬时均已解除<ref name="RW22">{{cite report | date = 2013-10-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714125653/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/declara-la-secretar%C3%ADa-de-gobernaci%C3%B3n-fin-de-la-emergencia-para-nueve-municipios-del-0 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | title = Declara la Secretaría de Gobernación fin de la emergencia para nueve municipios del estado de Michoacán | work = Cruz Roja Mexicana | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/declara-la-secretar%C3%ADa-de-gobernaci%C3%B3n-fin-de-la-emergencia-para-nueve-municipios-del-0 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-08-30 }}</ref><ref name="RW23">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150830033042/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/declara-la-secretar%C3%ADa-de-gobernaci%C3%B3n-fin-de-la-emergencia-para-21-municipios-del-1 | title = Declara la Secretaría de Gobernación fin de la Emergencia para 21 municipios del estado de Jalisco | work = Cruz Roja Mexicana | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2013-10-12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/declara-la-secretar%C3%ADa-de-gobernaci%C3%B3n-fin-de-la-emergencia-para-21-municipios-del-1 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | archivedate = 2015-08-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

墨西哥设立了32个灾害评估委员会，协助估算和分析公共基础设施所受破坏的价值，还有小组委员会协助估算学校、房屋和供水设施的损失<ref name="SG" />。奇尔潘辛戈和阿卡普尔科各开设了10个避难所<ref name="EU7" /><ref name="EU9">{{cite news | title = Ayudan a damnificados a través de puente aéreo | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-17 | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417063346/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/acapulco-guerrero-ayuda-aerea-lluvias-951025.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/acapulco-guerrero-ayuda-aerea-lluvias-951025.html | archivedate = 2014-04-17 }}</ref>。所有在拉平塔达泥石流灾害中幸存的村民都被转送至阿卡普尔科的篮球场，每人还拿到150美元的抚恤金<ref name="BBC 2" />。由于阿卡普尔科机场的商用航班停飞，[[墨西哥国际航空|墨西哥国际航空]]和英特捷特航空提供专机用于运送援助物资<ref name="RW7" />。
