截至9月18日，格雷罗州已经恢复供电<ref name="EU27">{{cite news | title = Restablece Telmex servicios de voz y datos en Guerrero | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/finanzas-cartera/2013/telmex-servicios-guerrero-951782.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503070159/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/finanzas-cartera/2013/telmex-servicios-guerrero-951782.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。阿卡普尔科也在当天恢复供水和燃气服务<ref>{{cite news | title = Regularizan abasto de gasolina y agua en Acapulco | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-18 | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/regularizan-abasto-de-gasolina-y-agua-en-acapulco-951845.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224195116/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/regularizan-abasto-de-gasolina-y-agua-en-acapulco-951845.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | archivedate = 2014-02-24 }}</ref>。安戈斯图拉和纳沃拉托要求宣示为灾区以获取联邦援助<ref>{{cite news | title = Malova pedirá declaratoria de emergencia por Manuel | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/malova-sinaloa-manuel-951940.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-09-19 | archivedate = 2014-02-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140204053810/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/malova-sinaloa-manuel-951940.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴第2次登陆后不到12小时，锡那罗亚州已有2万6000套住宅恢复供电<ref name="EU31">{{cite news | title = Restablecen 23% de luz en Sinaloa tras Manuel | date = 2013-09-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140218221447/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/cfe-sinaloa-electricidad-952119.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/cfe-sinaloa-electricidad-952119.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2014-02-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。因面临另一场泥石流的威胁，拉平塔达的搜救工作不得不暂停<ref name="RW7" />，但到9月20日时，100名救援人员已经恢复搜救工作，为了挖出遇难者遗体，他们经常需要挖开淤泥<ref name="RW8" />。

媒体批评墨西哥政府对两场飓风准备不足，其中一份报纸称政府“缺乏协调”，而且把精力分散在“周末的独立日庆典”上，低估了两场风暴的威胁<ref name="TT" />。多家媒体指责格雷罗州州长[[安吉尔·阿吉雷·里韦罗|安吉尔·阿吉雷]]（{{lang|es|ángel Aguirre}}）在曼努埃尔首度对该州构成威胁时还在持续通宵的聚会上饮酒作乐。阿吉雷之后发表电视讲话，承认自己涉身[[政治腐败|政治腐败]]，而且州内还有许多酒店和民房修筑在不安全的地方。[[墨西哥参议院|墨西哥参议院]]因此要求对情况展开调查。<ref name="UPI">{{cite news | title = Mexican officials under fire for storm preparation | date = 2013-09-27 | agency = United Press International}}</ref>

为了配合救援工作，墨西哥陆军和海军陆战队对房屋被淹的家庭提供帮助<ref name="EU1" />。此外，军方还向阿卡普尔科提供了60吨粮食和8000升水<ref name="RW3">{{cite news | title = Mexico death toll rises to 80 as new storms loom | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-death-toll-rises-80-new-storms-loom | agency = Agence France-Presse | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | author = Leticia Pineda | date = 2013-09-18 | publisher = ReliefWeb | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503182606/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-death-toll-rises-80-new-storms-loom | archivedate = 2014-05-03 }}</ref>，并设立航空基地空运援助物资<ref name="EU9" />。有关部门加紧清理两条高速公路上的石块及其它垃圾，以便恢复阿卡普尔科同外界的交通联系<ref name="RW4" />。超市在飓风过后出现[[抢购|抢购]]<ref name="RW4" />，阿卡普尔科有许多愤怒的灾民开始冲进商店、豪华酒店甚至他人的家里抢劫，海军陆战队员因此在多家商店外站岗，制止更多的盗窃活动<ref name="NBCN" />。[[墨西哥总统|墨西哥总统]][[恩里克·佩尼亚·涅托|恩里克·佩尼亚·涅托]]走访了大部分灾区，承诺重建阿卡普尔科和拉平塔达<ref name="BBC">{{cite news | title = Mexico storms: Village landslide missing 'probably dead' | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-24191716 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140217215442/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-24191716 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | newspaper = BBC News | date = 2013-09-21 | archivedate = 2014-02-17 }}</ref>。2014年5月26日，拉平塔达已建好125套新居，重新对外界开放<ref name="YE" />。
{{commons category|Aftermath of Hurricane Manuel in Acapulco|阿卡普尔科在飓风曼努埃尔过后的善后工作}}

飓风曼努埃尔对墨西哥造成严重破坏，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]因此决定将其名称除名，今后永远都不会再在东北太平洋风暴命名时采用。用于取代的新名称是“马里奥”，计划于2019年太平洋飓风季首度使用。<ref>{{cite report | title = WMO retires Ingrid and Manuel for Atlantic and eastern North Pacific basins | date = 2014-04-10 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2014/20140410_hurricanenameretired.html | accessdate = 2015-08-30 | archivedate = 2015-07-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150716082622/http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2014/20140410_hurricanenameretired.html }}</ref>

